      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_3",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "t the age of four, while her little pals were running about, aughing mehe",
        "bbox": [
          0.04725586959772693,
          0.21916519694297473,
          0.19979063855241513,
          0.2883009994121105
        ],
        "order": 5
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_4",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Another childhood memory is of Sunday afternoons, when other mums and dads were out for a stroll after lunch and her parents, Pat and Pip, would be holding a seance to commune with the other side.",
        "bbox": [
          0.047854045162255124,
          0.2887713109935332,
          0.16031105129355466,
          0.38612580834803056
        ],
        "order": 6
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_5",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Emma, 48, now a full-1 time witch, says: \"It seemed normal for me to see – and play with – dead people from the age of just four.",
        "bbox": [
          0.04845222072678331,
          0.38753674309229863,
          0.1686855091969493,
          0.44585537918871254
        ],
        "order": 7
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_6",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "\"My first time was at Hampton Court, but ever since then, it's happened regularly. My younger brother Ben and I knew our parents were different, but then, aren't everyon",
        "bbox": [
          0.047854045162255124,
          0.44632569077013523,
          0.16210557798713923,
          0.5239271017048794
        ],
        "order": 8
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_7",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "She says she inherited her mum's magical powers and \"came out of the closet – the broom closet\" after her parents died from cancer in 2019 and 2020.",
        "bbox": [
          0.04845222072678331,
          0.5248677248677248,
          0.21474502766561987,
          0.5737801293356849
        ],
        "order": 9
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_8",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Sh says: \"I'm the real-life Molly Weasley. Everyone calls me that.\"",
        "bbox": [
          0.047854045162255124,
          0.5836566725455614,
          0.20577239419769702,
          0.6527924750146973
        ],
        "order": 10
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_9",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "But, unlike the Harry Potter witch, she is a thoroughly modern Molly, with 96,000 followers on Insta- gram and 40,000 on TikTok.",
        "bbox": [
          0.04845222072678331,
          0.6532627865961199,
          0.1579183490354419,
          0.7214579659024103
        ],
        "order": 11
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_10",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "And she recently cast her spell on 262 would-be magic makers from across the world, initiating them as witches in on big, free Zoom session.",
        "bbox": [
          0.04845222072678331,
          0.7223985890652558,
          0.16150740242261102,
          0.7905937683715462
        ],
        "order": 12
      }
    ]
