        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Her husband is also on \"team witch\", says Emma, whose website has attracted clients wanting help with everything from mental health to fertility issues.",
        "bbox": [
          0.7800209361447585,
          0.8202233980011758,
          0.9552863765515178,
          0.8681951793062904
        ],
        "order": 20
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_23",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Emma says: \"When I tel people I'm a witch, the majority are fascinated and love hearing about what I do, from helping people find happi- ness to healing e,even helping them conseive ef 25 years 心 ago.\"",
        "bbox": [
          0.414535666218035,
          0.8300999412110524,
          0.5419470614625392,
          0.9613168724279836
        ],
        "order": 21
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_19",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "daughter Holly, then son Harry three years later.",
        "bbox": [
          0.2841333931508898,
          0.8507936507936508,
          0.4055630327501122,
          0.8799529688418577
        ],
        "order": 22
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_14",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "A tarot reader had told her she and Steve, then also 17 and an art student like her, would never have children.",
        "bbox": [
          0.0490503962913115,
          0.8606701940035273,
          0.1627037535516674,
          0.9091122868900646
        ],
        "order": 23
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_25",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "She has faced hostility from people saying she will \"go to hell for working for the devil\", but Emma says being a witch is \"posi- tive and nat- ural\".And she",
        "bbox": [
          0.6879018992074174,
          0.86114050558495,
          0.772244653805892,
          0.9584950029394473
        ],
        "order": 24
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_26",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "",
